typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		author as string,
		course as string,
		modifiedAt as timestamp 'yyyy-MM-dd\'T\'HH:mm:ss.SSS\'Z\'',
		progress as integer
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	limit: 100,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	dateFormats: ['yyyy-MM-dd'],
	timestampFormats: ['yyyy-MM-dd\'T\'HH:mm:ss.SSS\'Z\''],
	preferredIntegralType: 'integer',
	preferredFractionalType: 'double',
	booleanFormat: ['True', 'False']) ~> attempts
attempts filter(isNull('modifiedAt')) ~> filterNotNullModifiedAt
filterNotNullModifiedAt sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	input(
		author as string,
		course as string,
		modifiedAt as string,
		progress as string
	),
	umask: 0022,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	saveOrder: 1) ~> attemptsWithoutNullModifiedAt
